----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Log Analytics Agent
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Natural language → Elasticsearch DSL → Plain English answer
Ask questions about your logs in plain English. Get real answers backed by live data.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Overview
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Log Analytics Agent is a local, secure, and deterministic AI-powered observability tool that converts natural language queries into Elasticsearch DSL, executes them, and returns human-readable insights.

It is designed with:

Deterministic outputs (temperature = 0)
Security-first DSL validation
Template-based optimization (skip LLM when possible)
Local LLM execution (no data leaves your machine)


